        "product_description": {
            "value": "Bring the magic of Disney's Frozen to playtime with the Elsa Styling Mini Head. Standing 7 inches tall, this compact styling head features the beloved Snow Queen Elsa, ready for hours of imaginative pretend play. Perfect for young fans who love to create beautiful hairstyles, this mini styling head is ideal for on-the-go fun and smaller play spaces. Made from durable plastic, it captures Elsa's iconic look and invites children to comb, style, and design her hair again and again. Encouraging creativity and role play, this styling head helps develop fine motor skills and imaginative storytelling inspired by the enchanting world of Frozen. Designed for kids ages 3 and up, it makes a wonderful gift for any Frozen enthusiast. Whether recreating favorite movie moments or inventing brand-new adventures, little stylists will delight in caring for Elsa. A must-have addition to any Disney Frozen collection.",
